q1 )we have two slave servers how can we install webserver in two server
one is amazon linux
one is ubuntu  write a playbook for it

based on OS  amazon linux - httpd
             ubuntu   - apache2
vim condition.yml
---
- hosts: all
  connection: ssh

  tasks:
    - name: install webserver on RedHat
      yum: name=httpd state=present
      when: ansible_os_family=="RedHat"

    - name: install webserver on Ubuntu
      apt: name=apache2 state=present
      when: ansible_os_family=="Ubuntu"
...

ansible-playbook condition.yml

